  "time_ut": 1657340632,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u2019 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The struggle for 'the whole country for Colombo' is intense",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The protest being carried out today (09) in Colombo under the theme of \"The whole country is for Colombo\" is currently intensifying.",
        "People from different parts of the country have flocked to Colombo to participate in this protest.",
        "Demonstrations are being held in various parts of the country in support of the protest for \"All over Colombo\". Civil society, university students and trade unions have also supported this protest.",
        "In this case, security has been strengthened by the police, army and special task force in the protest area which is being carried out in Colombo - Gallimugat."
      ],
